<br>
I play Aadyn Tasurdyr, the leader of the Emerald Family. I just wanted to invite you to post information about your guild on a new messageboard I set up, <!--EZCODE LINK START--><a href="http://pub20.ezboard.com/bguildsoffirionavie13114" target="top">the Guilds of Firiona Vie</a><!--EZCODE LINK END--> (GoFV for short). <br>
<br>
At one time there was a guildlist that had been maintained by Nairda, which let people know some basic information about the various guilds on our server. It was a useful resource for the Firiona Vie community, but unfortunately it no longer seems to be maintained. I set up the GoFV messageboard in hopes that I could replicate and perhaps even improve upon Nairda's guildlist by making a lower maintenance and comprehensive alternative.<br>
<br>
Please feel free to post whatever information you see fit about Chivalorous Valor, as well as information about any recruiting drives or other events that Chivalorous Valor is having at any particular point. Also, I appreciate any suggestions you might have about how to make the board better, and would love any volunteers that may want to help moderate the board (although there does not seem to be a lot of moderating needed).<br>
<br>
Thanks for listening, and I hope you enjoy the board.<br>
